This guidebook will walk you through the basics of programming your Slay the Spire mod.

1. Basic Overview

Hi. Hopefully you've already followed the basic step-by-step instructions in README file. If not, go do those. In order.

If you ever need help beyond this guide, feel free to join the Slay the Spire discord! The modding community (found in the
#modding-technical channel) are happy to help for most things (as long as you're willing to listen.)
Here's a link: https://discord.gg/yWrmtJj5rT

Okay. So you've gone and renamed a bunch of things and now you're looking to make a Slay the Spire mod. STEP ONE DONE!

Step two is to look at cards. Try Strike, Defend, and the cards in 'democards/simple'.